# REPLACING THE WORDS WITH SIMILAR MEANING TO ONE WORD
categories = ['Clear','Cloudy','Snow','Rain','Drizzle','Fog','Thunderstorms','Haze']

df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace='Mainly Clear',value='Clear',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace='Mostly Cloudy',value='Cloudy',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace=['Snow Showers','Snow,Blowing Snow','Rain,Snow','Freezing Drizzle,Snow',
                                          'Freezing Rain,Snow Grains','Snow,Ice Pellets','Moderate Snow','Rain,Snow,
                                          'Ice Pellets','Drizzle,Snow','Rain Showers,Snow Showers','Moderate Snow,
                                          'Blowing Snow','Snow Pellets','Rain,Snow Grains'],value='Snow',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace=['Rain Showers','Freezing Rain','Rain,Ice Pellets'],value='Rain',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace='Freezing Drizzle',value='Drizzle',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace=['Rain,Fog','Drizzle,Fog','Snow,Fog','Drizzle,Snow,Fog','Freezing Drizzle,Fog',
                                          'Freezing Fog','Snow Showers,Fog','Freezing Rain,Fog','Thunderstorms,
                                          'Rain Showers,Fog','Rain Showers,Fog','Thunderstorms,Moderate Rain Showers,Fog',
                                          'Rain,Snow,Fog','Moderate Rain,Fog','Freezing Rain,Ice Pellets,Fog','Drizzle,
                                          'Ice Pellets,Fog','Thunderstorms,Rain,
                                          'Fog'],value='Fog',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace=['Thunderstorms,Rain Showers','Thunderstorms,Rain','Thunderstorms,
                                          'Heavy Rain Showers'],value='Thunderstorms',inplace=True)
df1.Weather_Condition.replace(to_replace=['Snow,Haze','Rain,Haze','Freezing Drizzle,Haze','Freezing Rain,Haze',],
                                         value='Haze',inplace=True)
